      "text": "The next stage of the crisis would be a global hegemony crisis when it comes to the dispute over which of today's currencies will become the world currency of the future, the currency of trade and reserves, the currency of financial transactions and, above all, the currency in which the lifeblood of the industrial and post-industrial age, oil, will be invoiced. [...] Without fierce political conflicts, this question will not be answered."
